    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Rewrite the following prospect brief so it is grammatically flawless and reads as a polished, professional sales report with smooth, natural flow. The company is a PROSPECT (a potential n8n customer) — keep that framing; never describe it as a tool inside n8n. Preserve ALL facts and figures, the automation-readiness score line, every section heading that has content (Research, Automation-Readiness Assessment), the rationale, the why-they-fit points, the automation opportunities, and all bullet points. Do not invent anything or add new claims. Omit any heading or section that has no content beneath it. Output the raw markdown directly — do NOT wrap it in code fences or triple backticks. Return ONLY the cleaned-up markdown.\n\n{{ $json.enriched_brief }}",
        "batching": {}
      },
